snippet.title: Minecraft Story Mode Episode 4: A Block and a Hard Place trailer
snippet.description:
Minecraft: Story Mode Episode 4 will be available to download on December 22nd, 2015!

Minecraft: Story Mode is a narrative-driven video game by Telltale Games, set in the world of Minecraft. Learn more at https://www.telltalegames.com/minecraftstorymode/
